WEBVTT

00:02:28.916 --> 00:02:32.246
all of the gastrointestinal,
neurological and cardiac symptoms --

00:02:32.715 --> 00:02:35.433
were being caused
by some distant emotional trauma

00:02:35.457 --> 00:02:37.063
that I could not remember.

00:02:38.069 --> 00:02:40.067
The symptoms were real, he said,

00:02:40.546 --> 00:02:42.905
but they had no biological cause.

00:02:44.527 --> 00:02:47.136
I was training to be a social scientist.

00:02:47.160 --> 00:02:50.392
I had studied statistics,
probability theory,

00:02:50.416 --> 00:02:52.990
mathematical modeling,
experimental design.

00:02:55.058 --> 00:02:59.051
I felt like I couldn't just reject
my neurologist's diagnosis.

00:02:59.599 --> 00:03:01.191
It didn't feel true,